      "rationale": "Force and displacement residuals converged to below 1e-5 for all 11 simulation cases. Newton-Raphson iteration with line search; no unconverged load steps recorded."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Use error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation inputs and boundary conditions reviewed by independent analyst; model setup documented in a controlled simulation plan.",
      "rationale": "Simulation plan reviewed and approved by a second FEA engineer independent of the model developer. Boundary conditions, material assignments, and contact definitions verified against the documented F1717 test fixture geometry."
