      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Constitutive model selection justified by material characterization data; contact formulation appropriate for the implant interface.",
      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening plasticity model calibrated from Ti-6Al-4V coupon tensile data (n=5). Augmented Lagrangian contact with friction coefficient 0.2 applied at rod-screw interface, consistent with published tribological data for titanium alloy pairs."
