      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions span the range of clinically relevant loading scenarios or a justification is provided for single-condition testing.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single load offset (44 mm) per ASTM F1717. Multiple load offsets were not evaluated. This factor is below the required level; the limitation is accepted given that F1717 specifies the single-offset protocol and clinical loading is bounded by this configuration."
