      "rationale": "E/uval computed for stiffness (0.87), yield force (1.41), and force at 40 mm (1.02). All three QoIs satisfy the pre-specified threshold of 1.96. Percentage differences also within the 10% bound. Comparison performed blind to experimental results prior to unblinding."
